comments.body:
hi @plantain-00 in case I move the code into 2 files, then there is one problem:
in the official pdfmake's documentation I should use this code:
```
for client-side use:
require ('pdfmake/build/pdfmake.js');
and require ('pdfmake/build/vfs_fonts.js');
```

or:
```
import * as pdfMake from 'pdfmake/build/pdfmake';
import * as fonts from 'pdfmake/build/vfs_fonts';
```
but I can't give 'pdfmake/build/pdfmake' name to some file. Whether it is possible to solve this problem?
